spans.text: Wake into Voice each silent String , And sweep the sounding Lyre
the loud Trumpet sound , Till the Roofs all around The shrill Echoes rebound
! the Numbers , soft and clear , Gently steal upon the Ear
her kindred Trees Descend from Pelion to the Main
the Infernal Bounds Which flaming Phlegeton
Thus Song could prevail Over Death and over Hell , A Conquest
